OL,3,CBereaved Israeli and Palestinian
OL,4,Cfathers now call each other brother
OL,6,FTwo bereaved fathers, one Israeli and
OL,7,Fone Palestinian, are using their
OL,8,Ffriendship to campaign for peace
OL,9,Fbetween their two nations.
OL,11,FDespite having fought for opposing
OL,12,Fsides as young men, Rami Elhanan and
OL,13,FBassam Aramin say they are now
OL,14,F"family" and have dedicated their
OL,15,Flives to building respect and
OL,16,Funderstanding between their
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,19,FThe two men were in Dublin to speak at
OL,20,Fan event hosted by the charity
OL,21,FTrocaire.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
