CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776643375
OL,3,CBereaved Israeli and Palestinian
OL,4,Cfathers now call each other brother
OL,6,FThey have visited the country before,
OL,7,Ftouring the island and sharing their
OL,8,Fstories last summer.
OL,10,F"I'm proud that he considers me a
OL,11,Fbrother," Mr Elhanan says of Mr Aramin.
OL,13,FThe 76-year-old veteran of the Yom
OL,14,FKippur War described a man who, aged
OL,15,F17, was jailed for throwing hand
OL,16,Fgrenades at Israeli jeeps.
OL,18,FMr Elhanan's life changed
OL,19,F"dramatically" following the death of
OL,20,Fhis 14-year-old daughter in 1997.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@IO]{D@AOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
