OL,3,CBereaved Israeli and Palestinian
OL,4,Cfathers now call each other brother
OL,6,FSmadar Elhanan was killed by
OL,7,FPalestinian suicide bombers while
OL,8,Fshopping for school books with friends
OL,9,Fin Jerusalem.
OL,11,FThe following year he was invited to a
OL,12,Fmeeting of bereaved Palestinian and
OL,13,FIsraeli parents, set up by The Parents
OL,14,FCircle ` Families Forum (PCFF), a
OL,15,Fjoint Israeli-Palestinian organisation
OL,16,Ffor bereaved families.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776643375
OL,3,CBereaved Israeli and Palestinian
OL,4,Cfathers now call each other brother
OL,6,F"I was very suspicious... I was very
OL,7,Freluctant and cynical," he said, but
OL,8,Fadded that the meeting "changed my
OL,9,Flife, changed my mind, changed my
OL,10,Fattitude".
OL,12,F"I was 47-years-old, and until today,
OL,13,FI'm ashamed to admit it was the first
OL,14,Ftime ever in my life I'd met
OL,15,FPalestinians as human beings, not as
OL,16,Fworkers in the streets, and not as
OL,17,Fterrorists, but as human beings who
OL,18,Fcarry the same burden that I carry,
OL,19,Fwho suffer like I suffer."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@WO]pD@XOUrD@IO]tD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
