OL,3,CBereaved Israeli and Palestinian
OL,4,Cfathers now call each other brother
OL,6,FHe became involved in grassroots peace
OL,7,Fmovements and met Mr Aramin through
OL,8,Fthe group Combatants for Peace in 2005.
OL,10,F"He always said that I immediately
OL,11,Ffell in love with him the minute I met
OL,12,Fhim, which is completely true," Mr
OL,13,FElhan said of Mr Aramin.
OL,15,FThat love was needed when, two years
OL,16,Flater, Mr Aramin's 10-year-old
OL,17,Fdaughter, Abir, was shot by the
OL,18,FIsraeli military in East Jerusalem.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776643375
OL,3,CBereaved Israeli and Palestinian
OL,4,Cfathers now call each other brother
OL,6,F"We ran to the hospital," Mr Elhanan
OL,7,Fsaid: "We spent two days by her bed
OL,8,Funtil she passed away and for me, it
OL,9,Fwas like losing my daughter for the
OL,10,Fsecond time, I knew this girl."
OL,12,FSince then the men have campaigned
OL,13,Ftogether, sharing their personal
OL,14,Ftragedies as a warning, and their
OL,15,Ffriendship as a symbol of hope.
OL,17,F"We proved that we can build a real
OL,18,Fpartnership, we can live together all
OL,19,Fside by side," Mr Elhanan said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@YO]oD@GOUrD@_O]yD@AOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
