OL,3,CBereaved Israeli and Palestinian
OL,4,Cfathers now call each other brother
OL,6,F"I see the goal very clearly, very
OL,7,Fsharply, I know exactly where I'm
OL,8,Fgoing, what needs to be done in order
OL,9,Fthat children will not keep on dying
OL,10,Fin this Holy Land of ours, no Muslim
OL,11,Fchildren, no Christian children, no
OL,12,FJewish children, no children at all."
OL,14,FA 2020 novel Aperiogon, based on the
OL,15,Fpair's friendship and written by Irish
OL,16,Fauthor Colum McCann, was longlisted
OL,17,Ffor the Booker prize.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
