PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776643375
OL,3,CBereaved Israeli and Palestinian
OL,4,Cfathers now call each other brother
OL,6,FThey compare coming to Ireland to a
OL,7,Ffootball team playing a home match,
OL,8,Fwith Mr Aramin saying people in the
OL,9,Fcountry "understand us, they're very
OL,10,Fsupportive".
OL,12,FThey say they use the peace that has
OL,13,Fbeen achieved in Northern Ireland as a
OL,14,Fstory of hope.
OL,16,F"It's not written anywhere that we're
OL,17,Fgoing to continue killing each other
OL,18,Fforever," Mr Aramin said.
OL,20,F"It must end at one point, and I
OL,21,Fbelieve very soon."
OL,26,@qD@IOUrD@KO]xD@AOUzD@IO]|D@AOU}D@SO]
